accTitle: Mermaid critical regions
accDescr {
Demonstrates Mermaid critical and option fragments mapped onto sequencer fragment branches.
From the project root, regenerate this Mermaid transform and SVG with:
node sequencer.js --mermaid -i test/mermaid-features/11-critical-regions/input.mmd -o -f -t test/mermaid-features/11-critical-regions
}
